<h2 id="from-what-i-knew-just-three-months-ago-im-seeing-remarkable-development" class="cnvs-block-section-heading cnvs-block-section-heading-1631597514200 is-style-cnvs-block-section-heading-2 halignleft" >
	<span class="cnvs-section-title">
		<span>From what I knew just three months ago, I&#8217;m seeing remarkable development.</span>
	</span>
</h2>



<p>I wouldn&#8217;t have believed it if someone told me a few months ago that I&#8217;d be composing and notating a 2-minute solo piece. Three months ago, I was having difficulty reading music scores, using software like Sibelius, and understanding some musical concepts.   My tutor told me that it was normal and that I should expect a learning curve, but I had not anticipated making such rapid progress in such a short period of time.</p>



<p>I learned a lot about scales and, in particular, how melodies are made. I had a lot of fun analyzing everything from simple ancient melodies to more complicated and contemporary ones, which helped me with my Assignment 2 composition.</p>


